==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Texas Leaguer
<hw>Tex"as Leagu"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[From the Texas (baseball)
League.]</ety> <fld>(Baseball)</fld> <def>A short fly that falls too far
out to be handled by an infielder and too close in to be caught by an
outfielder; -- called also <altname>Texas league single</altname>.</def>
<mark>[Cant]</mark>⟦br⟧
